---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Support — Pinochle Pro"
  description="Get help with Pinochle Pro. Submit feedback, vote on features, or contact us directly."
  canonical="/support"
>
  <h1 class="title">Support</h1>

  <p>If you have any questions, feedback, or need assistance with Pinochle Pro, we'd love to hear from you! Visit our <a href="https://pinochle-pro.canny.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">feedback site</a> to see what we're working on, submit ideas, and vote on other people's ideas.</p>

  <p>If you prefer to contact us directly via email, you can reach us at <a href="mailto:support@blackpanthersoftware.com">support@blackpanthersoftware.com</a>.</p>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Manage Your Subscription</h2>
    <p>If you subscribed to Pinochle Pro and need to upgrade, downgrade, or cancel your subscription, you can do so through your account portal.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="https://billing.revenuecat.com/portal" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="pricing-cta">Manage Subscription →</a>
    </p>
    <p><small>You can also manage your iOS subscription through <strong>Settings → Apple ID → Subscriptions</strong> on your iPhone or iPad.</small></p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <p>Check our <a href="/faq">FAQ page</a> for answers to common questions about gameplay, subscriptions, and the app.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
